Level System & Progression

Levels every 10 correct answers
Dynamic background colors that change by level
Special visual effects at high levels (level 8+ has iridescent background)
Free clues as level-up rewards

Survival Mechanics (Lives Mode)
Three ways to gain lives:

Accumulation: Correct answers (progression: 10, 20, 33, 47...)
Streaks: Consecutive correct answers (initial goal: 5, increases +2 each time)
ğŸ Prize Verbs: Randomly appear on irregular/reflexive verbs

