ğŸ§  Pedagogy & Content
Smart Filter System

6 verb tenses: Present, Simple Past, Present Perfect, Imperfect, Future, Conditional
11 irregularity types: From regular to completely irregular
Detailed educational tooltips for each grammatical concept
Hint system with progressive penalties

Content Adaptability

Manual verb selection or automatic filtering by characteristics
Score preview based on selected configuration
Dynamic balance between used/unused verbs

ğŸ® How to Play

Choose Game Mode: Time Attack, Survival, or Study Mode
Select Difficulty: ReCall, ConjugaATE, or Pr0ducâ‚¬
Configure Settings:

Select verb tenses to practice
Choose irregularity types or specific verbs
Select pronouns to include


Start Playing: Answer conjugation questions to build streaks and score points
Face Boss Battles: Every few questions, battle unique bosses with special mechanics
Track Progress: Watch your score climb and compete on global leaderboards

ğŸ† Scoring & Progression
Base Scoring

ReCall Mode: 5 points per correct answer
ConjugaATE Mode: 10 points per correct answer
Pr0ducâ‚¬ Mode: 15 points per correct answer

Bonuses

Speed Bonus: Answer quickly for extra points
Streak Multiplier: Build consecutive correct answers
Complexity Bonus: More tenses/pronouns/verbs = more points
Accent Bonus: +8 points for proper accent marks
Irregularity Bonus: +10 points per irregularity type
Boss Victory: +500 points (scales with boss reappearances)

ğŸµ Audio System
The game features a complete audio experience:

Background Music: Menu and game music with volume controls
Sound Effects: Feedback for correct/incorrect answers, boss battles, and special events
Character Voice: Chuache's reactions and commentary
Boss-Specific Audio: Unique sounds for each boss encounter

