Leaderboard System: Global score tracking


ğŸ¯ Educational Value
This game represents an excellent example of a "serious game" that:

Maintains user engagement during extended periods
Provides immediate pedagogical feedback
Adapts to different skill levels
Effectively gamifies the learning of complex linguistic structures

